Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.83,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　好运到来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.95,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　Paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:15.38,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元气弹一出手　炸裂吧飞散吧　Go Go Let's do it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:22.68,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘势力　正在某处蠢蠢欲动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:28.15,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不饶恕　全都给我等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:34.61,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豁出性命　我也一定守护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:40.44,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的勇气　要凭着它来令自己更强大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:46.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以坚持到底的气势　去跨越每一场危难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:53.79,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以遇强越强的气魄　更兴奋的我迎难而上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:58.09,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　好运到来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:01.26,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:06.85,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘着幸运的风  咻咻地飞越穹苍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:10.02,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　好运到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:13.14,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　明天依然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:20.32,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的灵魂　早已经知晓了所有的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到我这次变身的，你们都是头一个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利萨完成了新一阶段的变身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人绝望的强势攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在毫不留情地将短笛逼向绝路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟饭！可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着！你去也是白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如把我打成半死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就动手！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形势会发生逆转吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:38.51,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!Break!Care!Break!　随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:43.10,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着那无尽的天际飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:46.10,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高空中驾驭着喷射气流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:48.86,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪里　只要想去就去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:51.73,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水汽扑面而来　无比惬意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:54.99,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go tip-top!　All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:22:00.45,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝地球仿佛苏醒　睁开了眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:07.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗无可替代的星球　绝不能拱手放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:11.46,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧炸飞吧　龟派气功波
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.46,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个充满危机的时代里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:20.43,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着就要守护这世界　这是我的天命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.85,0:22:23.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!Break!Care!Break!　随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.39,0:22:26.60,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手一搏用尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:30.60,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为希望就是我拥有的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:35.28,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对未来我有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「弗利萨最后的超级变身！超越地狱的恐怖开始了」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟…悟饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊，悟饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢您，短笛叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼不该有这么强大的战斗力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从死亡边缘复苏过来后简直是判若两人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！那小鬼是赛亚人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，他是谁的孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十年前，除了贝吉塔、那巴和拉蒂兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以外的赛亚人应该都被我消灭干净了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像贝吉塔也不像那巴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉蒂兹的孩子吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有点像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚才那一下虽然被弹回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你真的变强了啊，悟饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我已经无能为力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使出了浑身的力气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却对弗利萨毫无作用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙也知道吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赛亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要从死亡边缘复活过来就会变强！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着弗利萨还没完成最后的变身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快把我打成半死！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快，动手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己动手是没有效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须由你来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭…凭我的力量怎么可能把你打成半死…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把战斗力压到最低
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭你的力量完全可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我们有那个一瞬间就能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好伤势的那美克星小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我再怎么讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我做这种事也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而…而且悟空马上就能复活了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡罗特是最下级战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会再变强了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须把赛亚人的血脉完全斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信什么超级赛亚人是史上最强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之类的无聊传说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在的形势可让我感觉不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上那小鬼和贝吉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也确实在不断地变强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，虽说以现在这个形态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能轻易将你们大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在临死之前还是让你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见识一下比死亡更恐怖的究极力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说究极的什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是特别优待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们能充分感受到超越地狱的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受一下我的真面目吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还来得及！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快动手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，管不了那么多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么软弱的攻击是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用更强的气打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这没用的废物！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终…终于能变成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超…超级赛亚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么小林叔叔要打伤贝吉塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟…悟饭 ，快离开这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧？短笛叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不能说完全没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您身上的伤可以治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫丹迪的那美克星人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会为您疗伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去叫他来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林叔叔，丹迪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不能为我疗伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你能治好其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不能治好我吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这家伙也杀了很多我们的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会为你这种人疗伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不治好我的伤，就没法打倒弗利萨！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我开始失去意识了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救那个人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭…小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉塔这样的赛亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要从死亡边缘复活过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能大幅提高自己的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道这一点吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那家伙故意让我弄伤他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像有信心打倒弗利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，贝吉塔！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听…听说…你会疗伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有这样的能力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你和内鲁哥哥一样，是战斗型的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪，你不想为贝吉塔疗伤的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过缺了他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就真的无能为力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙和弗利萨一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害了很多那美克星人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去为他疗伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我可以打倒贝吉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却对弗利萨无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事？是弗利萨吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙已经完成变身了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁机隐藏气息躲起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会把整个那美克星轰成碎末的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙对这颗星球已经没有任何留恋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好强的一股气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现…现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹…丹迪，拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给贝吉塔疗伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐看见他的身影了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该庆幸我没杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利萨的战斗力…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于露出真身了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，弗利萨你尽管放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在已经成为超级赛亚人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是弗利萨的真身？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体变小了，也干净利落了很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没什么迫力…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不能仅从外表判断实力的最佳范本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的他其实才可爱得多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得你们费尽千辛万苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用龙珠实现了愿望把我复活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我无论如何也救不了你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短笛叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有这种事，弗利萨的气又上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹…丹迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只感觉到一束光…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你们就别想再复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹…丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，究竟是怎么回事，完全猜不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的家伙，让他看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是靠丹迪才复活的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所…所以他就先拿他开刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究…究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是说好了嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让你们见识一下超越地狱的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，没法让那个那美克星小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一起品尝这种恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有些遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由你们代他充分体会这种恐怖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往哪逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶，这…这怎么可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在身后！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压倒性的力量逼向悟饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在终于露出真面目的弗利萨面前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众人只能束手待毙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
